            "original text": "We aimed to validate the observed differences in immune pathway expression at the protein level. We performed immunohistochemistry panels (c-MAF, CD8, CD14, CD20, CD45, and CD68) on 31 patients (25.8% from the metabolic-high group and 58.1% from the metabolic-low group)."
